    guid:
      Part1: 1731469969
      Part2: 1088413411
      Part3: 491232698
      Part4: 2994897401
    tag: 
  allNodes:
  - dialogueText: Hello, welcome to the hotel
    characterEmotion: 1
    characterReaction: 1
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952466358992965
    isRootNode: 1
    editorPosition: {x: 364, y: 280}
    guid:
      Part1: 1731469969
      Part2: 1088413411
      Part3: 491232698
      Part4: 2994897401
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Yes, how did you know?
    characterEmotion: 4
    characterReaction: 6
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses: []
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1367, y: 193.5}
    guid:
      Part1: 3718920237
      Part2: 1231748614
      Part3: 3489654206
      Part4: 3013054045
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: I'm not! At least not more than any ex-combatant, someone should
      look into what war does to a fellow's brain
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952466358992970
    - rid: 6774952466358992971
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1164, y: 453}
    guid:
      Part1: 4122052253
      Part2: 1305631986
      Part3: 1843491242
      Part4: 971911095
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: I didn't do it for you
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952466358992973
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2372, y: 569}
    guid:
      Part1: 3054298216
      Part2: 1109359958
      Part3: 2955129729
      Part4: 3364976297
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Not quite a troop, I wasn't doing much of the shooting. I prefer
      one bullet per brain, not three hundred misses to injure a single leg, ha!
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952466358992976
    - rid: 6774952466358992977
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2388, y: 239.5}
    guid:
      Part1: 49811686
      Part2: 1151970307
      Part3: 697042092
      Part4: 3722765143
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Oh, get over it
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses: []
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 3621, y: 372}
    guid:
      Part1: 1159698806
      Part2: 1178946090
      Part3: 445712812
      Part4: 798104986
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: If I didn't take light of having to kill my fellow compatriots
      in my desperate attempt to appease my superiors against constant defamations
      and attacks towards my persona... I would've left that place a long time before
      I was discharged
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952466358992980
    - rid: 6774952466358992981
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 3668, y: 94.52}
    guid:
      Part1: 2866881234
      Part2: 1269484422
      Part3: 2837742259
      Part4: 3537210373
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: I began to believe everyone was a a secret (secret (secret (secret)))
      spy! Crazy, right?
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952466358992983
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 5525, y: -7.9600067}
    guid:
      Part1: 1974382265
      Part2: 1165827636
      Part3: 405430694
      Part4: 3257180410
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Who's lying?
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 767062219271962632
    - rid: 767062219271962633
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1028.7688, y: -28.920502}
    guid:
      Part1: 3005462273
      Part2: 1186196420
      Part3: 3619405476
      Part4: 2018895431
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: I can tell from a mile away when someone is unpleasable, she's
      a lost couse as far as I'm concerned
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 767062219271962635
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1606.9999, y: -103.63126}
    guid:
      Part1: 3644508348
      Part2: 1196827177
      Part3: 70828988
      Part4: 2055379135
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: She's one of those people that won't change their mind about something,
      no matter the evidence against it.
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 767062219271962637
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2505.9998, y: -103.63126}
